  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dad\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dbd\u0ddd \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Brother Malo caught with illegal liquor",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kandaketiya Police raided a liquor factory run by two brothers in the Wewpitiya village in Karametiya, Meegahakiula and seized 45,000 ml of kassippu this afternoon (27).",
        "The suspects are aged 29 and 31 and are residents of Lihiniyamandiya, Wewpitiya, Karametiya.",
        "The two suspects were arrested during a raid carried out today (27) on a tip off received by the Kandaketiya Police Intelligence Bureau that the two were producing and selling illicit liquor in and out of the area.",
        "The suspects are to be released on police bail and a case will be filed against them in the Badulla court, police said. Kandaketiya police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
